---
title: Double Haloumi & Veggie Fritters with Roast Potatoes & Pear Salad
description: Welcome to your new number one meat-free dinner, it's top of the charts for a reason. Fritters are a great go-to because you can pack them with whatever goodies you like! These ones have corn and carrot, and they’re paired with a sweet and fresh pear salad to finish things off with a bang.

